name: podamCannotFillInterfaceAttributesIfTheExternalFactoryDoesNotManufactureTheRightType

testSteps.description: Given a Podam Factory with external factory uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1427ca8

Then the two objects uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1427ca8 and uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1427ca8 should be equal
When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.PojoWithInterfaces
Then the object uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.PojoWithInterfaces@879c1 should not be null
Then the two objects interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ObjectExt and interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ObjectExt should be equal
Then the two objects interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.InterfacePojo and interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.InterfacePojo should be equal
Then the two objects 0 and 0 should be equal

title: Podam cannot fill interface attributes if the external factory does not manufacture the right type
